        "content": "<p>Hi everyone,</p>\n<p>I was hoping to find a way to prove the following couple of statements in a line or two, but didn't turn anything up on my own. I appreciate any assistance!</p>\n<p>∀ (n : ℕ), n ∈ [1, 2, 3] → n &lt; 10 <br>\n∀ (n : ℕ), n ∈ [1, 2, 3] ∨ n ∈ [4, 5, 6] → n &lt; 10</p>",
